
-------------------------------eclipse ee-----------------------------------------------
最好的方法是去这个地址下载jre
http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jre8-downloads-2133155.html

然后在这个地址下载eclipse
http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/download.php?file=/technology/epp/downloads/release/mars/2/eclipse-jee-mars-2-linux-gtk-x86_64.tar.gz

两个傻逼下好以后，将eclipse解压到/home/chen/

然后把jre1.x.x 放进eclipse/，把版本号什么的去掉
然后运行程序图标就大功告成

注意的是工程是建在～/workspace里面的

编写C++：先下载下面的插件

http://www.eclipse.org/downloads/download.php?file=/tools/cdt/releases/8.8.1/cdt-8.8.1.zip


sudo cp –r cdt/plugins/ ～/java/eclipse/
sudo cp –r cdt/features/ ～/java/eclipse/

---------------------------------eclipse c++----------------------------------------------
安装g++编译器
sudo  apt-get  install build-essential
